name: GrandeBROW-LAMINATE Brow Styling Gel with Peptides
about: What it is:A brow styling gel that shapes, sculpts, and sets brows for an immediate fuller and lifted look, plus it conditions for healthier-looking brows over time..Highlighted Ingredients:- Myristoyl Pentapeptide-17.Ingredient Callouts:It is cruelty-free..What Else You Need to Know:The immediate lifting, sculpting, and setting benefits of professional brow lamination meets the nourishing power of peptides for conditioned looking brows over time. A bonus Pro-Brow Styling Brush is included..Clinical Results:Based on a 2-week consumer perception study with 32 subjects:
ingredients: -Myristoyl Pentapeptide-17..Aqua (Water), Ceteareth-30, Sucrose Stearate, Propanediol, Glycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Propylene Glycol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Citric Acid, Myristoyl Pentapeptide-17.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:.-Coat the spoolie brush with a small amount of styling gel. Wipe off any excess. Close lid tightly to maintain efficacy..-Brush styling gel through clean brows for a feathered, laminated look or for a natural, defined look..-After use, clean brush with warm water.
